Examples of fonts are at [@../../../svg_plot/example/demo_2d_fonts.cpp demo_2d_fonts.cpp].

Fine control of font family and size is provided,
although the exact rendering may be limited by the browser used to view the .svg file.

An example is provided to demonstrate various fonts and fonts sizes.

